VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT resource\s+"google_compute_instance"[^}]*access_config\s*\{
WHEN EXPR MISSING:nat_ip\s*=\s*""
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects GCP Compute Engine instances configured with external IP addresses via access_config blocks.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for GCP VM Instance with Public IP.
